::Prowl/Mosquitor/Striker/Zenyak/Shredder::

Prowl throws Mosquitor back into the clearing. Mosquitor an autogun hits the 
bug and he falls to the ground in a motionless heap.

Prowl chuckles as he walks over to Mosquitor and shoots him one more time to 
make sure he was out for the battle. He turns around and sees Rampage enter 
the Ark. Sword in one hand and gun in the other, Prowl follows him. 
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
The Striker and Zenyak stand on the bottom of the ocean, swords still 
swinging at each other. The water all around them was stained with mech fluid.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Shredder walks into the CR chamber, activating it. He relaxes as the CR 
chamber starts mending his wounds.
